subject: CBSNews.com News Alert! House Fails To Override Bush Veto
body:
The Democratic-controlled House has failed to override President Bush's veto 
of an Iraqi war spending bill with timetables for troop withdrawals. The 
222-203 vote fell far short of the two-thirds majority needed.
